data.description: Do you want to live close to the beaches and own your own land?  Look no further!!!  Iona Gardens is a sought-after community with no mandatory HOA fees and no age restrictions.  This perfect little GEM is located on a nice size lot with gates & fencing for privacy.  Lots of room to add a lanai, carport and additional storage.  This raised home offers two bedrooms, one full bath with tub/shower combo, inside washer & dryer.   The outside is the heart of this property with loads of room for parking, an open patio and room for your pets to run and play.  There is a community pool and the HOA is OPTIONAL for a low cost.  Iona Gardens is located just off McGregor and close to shopping, dining and entertainment.
